1. Install [YouCompleteMe](https://github.com/ycm-core/YouCompleteMe)
2. Install [zig.vim](https://github.com/ziglang/zig.vim)
3. Add these lines to your `.vimrc`:

```vim
let g:ycm_language_server =
    \\ [
    \\    {
    \\     'name': 'zls',
    \\     'filetypes': [ 'zig' ],
    \\     'cmdline': [ '/path/to/zls_executable' ]
    \\    }
    \\ ]
```

To apply in-editor configuration or manually specify the path to `zig`, please refer to the YCM [LSP Configuration Docs](https://github.com/ycm-core/YouCompleteMe?tab=readme-ov-file#lsp-configuration).
